{
  "id": "69b89a7e719400bfbc001c70",
  "title": "有気音・無気音・有声音・無声音",
  "created": 1773705871,
  "updated": 1773706366,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b89a7e719400bfbc001c70",
      "text": "有気音・無気音・有声音・無声音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773705871,
      "updated": 1773705871
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89a8e000000000023fa2d",
      "text": "日本語や英語は有声音と無声音の対立がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773705871,
      "updated": 1773705888
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89aa0000000000023fa2f",
      "text": "中国語や韓国語は有気音と無気音の対立がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773705888,
      "updated": 1773706111
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89ab0000000000023fa30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773705905,
      "updated": 1773705905
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89ab0000000000023fa31",
      "text": "上海語には無声無気音・無声有気音・有声音の対立がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773705905,
      "updated": 1773706125
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89bb0000000000023fa32",
      "text": "サンスクリット語・ヒンドゥー語には無声無気音・無声有気音・有声無気音・有声有気音の対立がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773706160,
      "updated": 1773706366
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89a98000000000023fa2e",
      "text": "\ttable:デーヴァナーガリー文字",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773705881,
      "updated": 1773706226
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89be9000000000023fa34",
      "text": "\t\tक\tख\tग\tघ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773706218,
      "updated": 1773706272
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89bf3000000000023fa35",
      "text": "\t\tk(a)\tkh(a)\tg(a)\tgh(a)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773706228,
      "updated": 1773706276
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89bf6000000000023fa36",
      "text": "\t\tk(ə)\tkʰ(ə)\tɡ(ə)\tɡʱ(ə)\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773706231,
      "updated": 1773706300
    },
    {
      "id": "69b89bdf000000000023fa33",
      "text": "\t字形も違いすぎる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773706208,
      "updated": 1773706289
    },
